            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Not sure if it's related but I'm getting treesitter issues as well when doing `vim.lsp.buf.hover()`:\n```   Error  04:24:32 msg_show.emsg Decoration provider \"conceal_line\" (ns=nvim.treesitter.highlighter):\nLua: /usr/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/treesitter.lua:196: attempt to call method 'range' (a nil value)\nstack traceback:\n\t/usr/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/treesitter.lua:196: in function 'get_range'\n\t/usr/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/treesitter.lua:231: in function 'get_node_text'\n\t...nvim-treesitter/lua/nvim-treesitter/query_predicates.lua:141: in function 'handler'\n\t/usr/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/treesitter/query.lua:868: in function '_apply_directives'\n\t/usr/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/treesitter/query.lua:1089: in function '(for generator)'\n\t/usr/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/treesitter/languagetree.lua:1123: in function '_get_injections'\n\t/usr/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/treesitter/languagetree.lua:690: in function '_parse'\n\t/usr/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/treesitter/languagetree.lua:639: in function 'parse'\n\t/usr/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/treesitter/highlighter.lua:529: in function </usr/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/treesitter/highlighter.lua:52\n```\n\nMy neovim version:\n```\nNVIM v0.12.0-dev-2690+g39bb5d7ca2\nBuild type: RelWithDebInfo\nLuaJIT 2.1.1772619647\nRun \"nvim -V1 -v\" for more info\n```\n\n~I get the same issue when running the deprecated nvim-treesitter `master` branch and the current `main` branch.~\n\nOk actually I updated nvim to the latest commit and made sure to uninstall all other treesitter related plugins and then fresh installed the `main` branch and my `vim.lsp.buf.hover()` issue is resolved.\n\nMy current neovim version:\n```\nNVIM v0.12.0-dev-2691+gebc9811149\nBuild type: RelWithDebInfo\nLuaJIT 2.1.1772619647\nRun \"nvim -V1 -v\" for more info\n```",
